<D>__{i guess there's always a chance.}
<A>__{the doors break open. noel comes flying out, bounces on the sidewalk. griss, in the doorway, closes the doors. mary goes over to noel:}
<C>__{mary}
<D>__{noel, noel, it's me, mary. from 17th street.}
<C>__{noel}
<D>__{mary, mary, mary. i'm so thirsty. they won't give me anything to drink. please, mary.}
<C>__{mary}
<P>__{(heading inside)}
<D>__{i will get you some.}
